Maria Tucci https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maria_Tucci 0 Maria Tucci (born June 19, 1941) is an Italian-American actress.She was nominated for the Tony Award for Best Featured Actress in a Play in 1967 for her performance in The Rose Tattoo. She played Koula in the 2015 mini-series The Slap.
